{"tid":814070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律面前] 林鄭:任何人詆毀法官或人身攻擊不能接受","createTime":"2018-09-11T02:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T03:35:12.000Z","uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dd64d80bb568f5bed2a15a3b186f5a6ac8ffbf67","tid":814070,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"終審法院上周裁定，反對新界東北發展撥款案中非法集結罪成的13名被告，刑期上訴得直。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>港區全國人大代表吳秋北事後在社交網站撰文，形容法官是「青年殺手，社會罪人」</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n對於這種批評法官言論，行政長官林鄭月娥出席行政會議前回應稱，就終審法院的裁決引起一些人士對法官的批評，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>甚至是對法官人身攻擊，她表示遺憾</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，不論政治立場，無論哪些人士就法庭裁決，作出不合適言論，不滿意法庭的裁決，就詆毀法官或蔑視司法制度，或人身攻擊某一位法官，都是不能接受，這對本港司法制度或司法精神都是一大損害。"},{"pid":"abb8b9fd8cb1d0c4262f9518034789ccf590caf9","tid":814070,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T03:06:43.000Z","msg":"痰罐人大有份屌法官喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0363876f2ee2a713136cb4e8b93b588f9d6df06b","tid":814070,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abb8b9fd8cb1d0c4262f9518034789ccf590caf9","tid":814070,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T03:06:43.000Z","msg":"痰罐人大有份屌法官喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T03:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過會出聲都幾unexpected"},{"pid":"353c8c96a4e05fd945a30bea83aa5edd4a7b5ede","tid":814070,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T03:12:55.000Z","msg":"吳秋北如果唔順氣可以出聲喎<br />\n<br />\n枉你咁愛港愛蟈<br />\n<br />\n到頭黎竟然俾人話返轉頭<br />\n<br />\n係我就爆seed 反擊返蛾蛆嘅批評喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係男人就唔好忍 除非你唔係<img src=\"/as